				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Quiet area away from the main streets. Somebody here has forgotten about her dead children, in blissful state.\r\n\r\nLug is peacefully looking over the bridge, softly singing a lullaby. If spoken to, she laughs and tells you she’s had this song suck in her head for some reason! She doesn’t know any children, how odd."
				}
